	<Title>
		Need motivation to exercise? Try a diary
	</Title>
	<Body>
		&lt;p&gt;Have you started a workout program? Good for you! Record your efforts to track progress toward your goals. After each workout, record these items: 1. The date. 2. Your activity (swimming, lifting weights, volleyball). 3. How long you exercised. 4. How you felt afterward. Having a chronicle of your improvement can be a great source of motivation.&lt;/p&gt;
